{
  "stem": "9701.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a German Jewish organization, or mostly Jewish, that had its headquarters across the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a lot of animosity towards that group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And perhaps because of that I thought, I have to find out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I went across the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And it's-- and I joined the organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it's there that I really got my political education, which has made me who I am today.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "One of the goals of that organization was to go back to Germany after the war and reeducate the German population in democratic principles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, you know, it was concerned about both the emotional and psychological well-being of people, but also to become actively involved in doing things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that has really been part of my life ever since.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's the lesson that I've taken from the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, many people or many survivors say, you know, why wasn't more done for us?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there are people in this world, in this city today who are suffering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And knowing what suffering is-- and mine certainly wasn't the worst, because I was never in a concentration camp-- I think it behooves me, it's my duty to become involved in the issues whereby I can maybe make a difference.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not going to be able to change the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think each and every one of us not only can but must make a difference.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't think any one of us is insignificant enough to not be able to do this, maybe very small things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I frequently talk to students.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I always urge them and challenge them to become involved in no matter what it is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe something in their school.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
